{"tid":1463434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"割咩𥱊？戴耀廷「佔領中環」仲激過「癱瘓機場」喎","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T14:50:25.000Z","uid":35870,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2cc2fdfb741fa21c1c9acff52672d4be7efe64","tid":1463434,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:07.000Z","msg":"明明「癱瘓機場」同「佔領中環」concept就一樣，結果就有d人出黎屌晒鬼話觀感唔好<br />\n<br />\n真係笑撚左，呢幾年係咁笑戴耀廷左膠，點知原來自己仲膠過戴耀延，真係正式宣佈戴耀延仲激過連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係講笑，戴耀廷個套可以諗諗呀，學佔領華爾街咁訓係地晒係下塞住個出入境<br />\n<br />\n嘩！真係讓愛與和平佔領機場！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69098ca9538074142343366563e50509ea17bd90","tid":1463434,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:13.000Z","msg":"利益伸報：唔鼓勵大家做犯法行為，純粹學術討論戴耀廷理論應用係今次嘅context"},{"pid":"4da620f189eff1f1c5f43b706e14b34836621454","tid":1463434,"uid":262389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456781</a>"},{"pid":"0b836164b0193c8970c87b2a1bf58674543fd779","tid":1463434,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d29d31cd04e48cde6b555db6758999ae5c1719","tid":1463434,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:24:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764b02754039cefb68ff632743e5d3662e9e0522","tid":1463434,"uid"